      "content": "Hey, I need some help looking at these discrepancies from our Q3 audit in the Rotterdam facility. We're seeing some weird gaps between the WMS and the physical count for these specific electronic modules. \n\nCan you look at this list and tell me what kind of common causes we should investigate?\n\nPart_ID | WMS_Count | Physical_Count | Variance\nELEC-992-X | 450 | 448 | -2\nELEC-441-B | 1200 | 1195 | -5\nELEC-002-Z | 85 | 83 | -2\nELEC-773-K | 310 | 309 | -1\nELEC-119-M | 55 | 52 | -3\n\nIt's not a huge amount, but it's happening every month.",
